cs.GT, cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.CC

This paper deals with the pricing schemes for Internet services, which involves game theory and network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Decision Making), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves information theory and communication complexity, which could fall under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
